commit.message: [trans] Update Translation

Rename all rime action icon to avoid wrong icon being used.

When a icon them only provides fcitx-rime icon or fcitx icon, based on
XDG fallback, fcitx-rime-* icon will be fallback to fcitx-rime, or even
fcitx.

An example in real world is breeze that doesn't have fcitx-rime-im icon.
Which make kimpanel shows two identical fcitx-rime icon.
